cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image denoising, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of skip connections is a common technique in neural networks, which falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper is also related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it deals with image processing.
